data.description: Mid-Century Modern in South Hills! Living room has architectural details not normally found in this area. Both living and family areas are spacious. Freshly painted interior, vaulted ceilings, wood-look laminate floors, carpet in bedrooms. Beautiful brick wood burning fireplace. Covered patio with mature shade trees! Convenient location to shopping and short drive to downtown Fort Worth.
